2011年10月30日，[[吉尔吉斯斯坦|吉尔吉斯斯坦]]提前舉行'''總統選舉'''<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/30/kyrgyzstan-election-idUSLDE75T02920110630 |title=Kyrgyz MPs set presidential election for Oct 30 |publisher=Reuters |date=2011-06-30 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2019-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213020543/https://www.reuters.com/article/kyrgyzstan-election/kyrgyz-mps-set-presidential-election-for-oct-30-idUSLDE75T02920110630 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，接替代理[[吉尔吉斯斯坦总统|總統]][[萝扎·奥通巴耶娃|萝扎·奥通巴耶娃]]。[[吉尔吉斯斯坦社会民主党|社會民主黨]]的前總理[[阿尔马兹别克·阿坦巴耶夫|阿尔马兹别克·阿坦巴耶夫]]在首輪選舉勝出而當選<ref name="PM wins">{{Citation |title=Kyrgyz PM wins presidential election |publisher=Al Jazeera English |date=2011-11-01 |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2011/10/2011103164540483122.html |accessdate=2011-11-06 |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109101649/http://english.aljazeera.net//news/asia/2011/10/2011103164540483122.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
[[2010年吉爾吉斯革命|去年的革命]]導致時任[[吉尔吉斯斯坦总统|總統]][[库尔曼别克·巴基耶夫|库尔曼别克·巴基耶夫]]被推翻<ref>{{cite web |author=F_363 |url=http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6944774.html |title=Presidential vote in Kyrgyzstan in 6 months: interim leader - People's Daily Online |publisher=English.people.com.cn |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68qkrlRuV?url=http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6944774.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[萝扎·奥通巴耶娃|萝扎·奥通巴耶娃]]領導的臨時政府在該年4月19日公佈修憲和選舉計劃<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rttnews.com/Content/PoliticalNews.aspx?Id=1272738&SM=1 |title=Kyrgyz Interim Government Unveils Reform Plan To 'return To Democracy' |publisher=Rttnews.com |date=2010-04-19 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68ql01K6d?url=http://www.rttnews.com/Story.aspx?type=pn |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根據新憲法，總統每屆任期為六年，但不得連任<ref>{{cite web|title=FACTBOX-Key political risks to watch in Kyrgyzstan - AlertNet|url=http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/factbox-key-political-risks-to-watch-in-kyrgyzstan|accessdate=2011-10-30|date=2010-10-01|publisher=Trust.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728144350/http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/factbox-key-political-risks-to-watch-in-kyrgyzstan|archivedate=2011-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 日期 ==
當局在2010年4月22日公佈總統選舉日期，同年6月的公投通過[[2010年吉爾吉斯修憲公投|修憲]]，縮減總統權力和推進民主<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8636577.stm |title=Kyrgyzstan's new leaders set October election date |work=BBC News |date=2010-04-22 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2010-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100425125713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8636577.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年5月19日，政府宣佈總統選舉將不會與[[2010年吉爾吉斯國會選舉|國會選舉]]同時舉行，而是押後至2011年10月，奥通巴耶娃將留任總統至2011年12月31日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldbulletin.net/news_detail.php?id=58755 |title=Kyrgyzstan's interim leader Otunbayeva to be president to 2011 | Asia-Pasific |publisher=World Bulletin |date=2010-05-19 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2012-07-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68ql0tOO9?url=http://www.worldbulletin.net/index.php?aType=haber |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 候選人 ==
中央選舉委員會表示，8月16日限期前有83人報名參選，當中16人是經政黨提名，其餘則自薦參選。參選人需要收集三萬個簽名、繳付十萬[[吉尔吉斯斯坦索姆|元]]、及通過語言測試<ref name="referl">{{cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/content/eighty-three_register_as_kyrgyz_presidential_candidates/24298438.html |title=Eighty-Three Candidates Declare For Kyrgyz Presidential Election |publisher=Rferl.org |date=2011-08-16 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102338/http://www.rferl.org/content/eighty-three_register_as_kyrgyz_presidential_candidates/24298438.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終16人成功通過上述條件而正式成為總統選舉候選人，當中包括<ref name="aljaz1">{{Cite web|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2011/10/20111030836831101.html|title=Kyrgyzstan votes for new president|website=english.aljazeera.net|access-date=2016-11-08|archive-date=2011-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111101202529/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2011/10/20111030836831101.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>：

* [[阿尔马兹别克·阿坦巴耶夫|阿尔马兹别克·阿坦巴耶夫]]<ref name="referl"/>：現任總理，因參選總統而在九月辭任[[吉尔吉斯斯坦社会民主党|吉尔吉斯斯坦社会民主党]]黨魁<ref name="aljaz2">{{cite web |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/video/asia/2011/10/201110288015547701.html |title=Anxiety marks Kyrgyzstan poll run-up - Asia |publisher=Al Jazeera English |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2011-10-30 |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109094615/http://english.aljazeera.net/video/asia/2011/10/201110288015547701.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC">{{cite news | url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-15510217 | work=BBC News | title=PM Atambayev wins Kyrgyzstan presidential election | date=2011-10-31 | accessdate=2020-11-18 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000835/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-15510217 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，因推動新{{tsl|en|Constitution of Kyrgyzstan|吉爾吉斯憲法|憲法}}而被視為「改革派持旗手」<ref name="aljazcontro">{{Cite web|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2011/10/20111030175330696330.html|title=Controversy mars Kyrgyz presidential election|website=english.aljazeera.net|access-date=2016-11-08|archive-date=2011-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103062259/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/asia/2011/10/20111030175330696330.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ；
* {{tsl|en|Kamchybek Tashiyev|金智白·泰斯耶夫}}：前緊急情況部長[[故乡_(政党)|故鄉黨]]黨魁<ref name="aljaz1" /> ；
* 亞達肯·馬杜馬洛夫：前國家安全首長<ref name="aljaz1" /> ；
* {{tsl|en|Kubatbek Baibolov|古白畢·拜博諾夫}}：前檢控總長<ref name="referl"/> ；
